{"type": "article", "id": 5961, "title": "Kubus 碗", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-06T07:33:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233900iVoysurGph94XjfQ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦人 Mogens Lassen 是建筑师出身，这款 Kubus Bowl 算是他关注功能性的代表作品，体现存储功能的半球形与利于支撑的立方体线框，形成强烈的视觉反差。日常器皿，应该具备一物多用的功能，它既可以盛放甜点、水果或是糖果，也可以作为花器植栽，当然你若是想要将碗与支架拆开来用，也未尝不可。此外，Kubus Bowl 还被提名为今年的德国设计大奖(German Design Award)，提供黑、白、灰、米色以及镀铜 5 种选择，定价 129－229 欧元（约合人民币 922－1636 元）不等，<a href=\"http://bylassen.com/shop/kubus-bowl-57c1.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052338592PQbRCluUyzoNTjO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233859t5i9ZlckoS6hM1ae.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233900k0rU3IwHNavMCEZg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}